t une interrogation sur la viabilité de la « manière d’être ensemble » dans les organisations d’Amérique latine, selon une expression consacrée par Philippe d’Iribarne.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Business Communication / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276371382340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763713823423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763713823/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles